com.amplifyframework.datastore

Class DataStoreItemChange<T extends Model>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.DataStoreItemChange<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the item that underwent changed

    public final class DataStoreItemChange<T extends Model>
extends java.lang.Object
    A DataStoreItemChange is emitted whenever there is a change to an item in the DataStore.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      static class  DataStoreItemChange.Builder<T extends Model>
      A utility to construct instances of DataStoreItemChange.
      static class  DataStoreItemChange.Initiator
      The initiator of the change.
      static class  DataStoreItemChange.Type
      A DataStoreItemChange can either be caused by a call to one of the DataStoreCategoryBehavior.save(Model, Consumer, Consumer) family of methods, or to one of the DataStoreCategoryBehavior.delete(Model, Consumer, Consumer) methods.
